      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this automotive specimen in exemplary condition. Maintained to a showroom standard, the vehicle exhibits pristine aesthetic preservation and absolute mechanical integrity. Every detail reflects a commitment to excellence, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning professional. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of this distinction.",
